data.description: BEST price for a gated community in this area - Don't miss out on the opportunity to live close to other townhouse communities that sell for much more! This traditional 2 bedroom 2.5 bathroom townhouse with a bonus room at the garage level, is ready for you to make it your own. Total sq ft is 1812! Both bedrooms have ensuite bathrooms and walk in closets. The half bath is on the main-floor living area with easy access for guests. Bright and airy space, for you to bring your modern, minimalist or continue the mid-century decor to live your life with full expression. If you don't already know the east Atlanta location, you will certainly enjoy getting to know the eclectic area that surrounds your new home.  You can enjoy the best of Intown living being in close proximity to East Atlanta Village Farmers Market, Ponce City Market, Grant Park, the east side Beltline, East Lake Golf Course and plenty of bars and restaurants. Public transport is also available nearby. Stop reading and take a look at our virtual tour so you can visit and get your offer in quickly!
